<div class="status-page">
  <h4 class="title">Status page URL</h4>
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="info-card__img--container">
      {{svg-jar "default-logo" class="info-card__img"}}
    </div>
    <div class="info-card__content">
      <h5 class="info-card__subtitle">Your public status page URL</h5>
      <a href="" class="info-card__link">
        https://acmeinc.status.freshservice.com
        {{svg-jar "open-new-tab" class="icon-new-tab"}}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h4 class="title">Enhance your status page: Effortlessly configure services, customizations, and subscribers!</h4>
  <div class="status-cards">
    <div class="status-card">
      <div class="status-card__img--container">
        {{svg-jar "manage" class="status-card__img"}}
      </div>
      <div class="status-card__content">
        <h4 class="title">Configure services</h4>
        <p class="status-card__content--paragragh">
          Effortlessly manage and customize your services to ensure accurate representation on the status
          page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="status-card">
      <div class="status-card__img--container">
        {{svg-jar "manage-subscriber" class="status-card__img"}}
      </div>
      <div class="status-card__content">
        <h4 class="title">Customize status page</h4>
        <p class="status-card__content--paragragh">
          Tailor your status page to align perfectly with your brand by personalizing content and appearance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="status-card">
      <div class="status-card__img--container">
        {{svg-jar "manage-subscriber" class="status-card__img"}}
      </div>
      <div class="status-card__content">
        <h4 class="title">Manage subscribers</h4>
        <p class="status-card__content--paragragh">
          Track and manage your Status page subscribers and the services they have subscribed
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="sidebar__container">
  <h4 class="title">Status page</h4>
  <p class="sidebar__content">The Status page serves as a communication tool for businesses, enabling them to offer
    transparency regarding service availability and significant outages, fostering trust with customers who can
    subscribe to receive service updates via email.</p>
</div>